data.name: Text_BoxDescription.Text
data.value:
SCCM PC Admin (originally called PC++) was created in January 2015 to perfect my skills as a programmer. It was initially designed to merge multiple tools created with different programming languages into a single application. In July 2016, a major overhaul of SCCM PC Admin was completed to include all the tools required to support SCCM on a remote computer.
Special thanks go out to: Simon Fortin: for assisting with translation and helping out with some of the programming components, Danny Gauthier : for assisting with translation, Chris Spadijer : For helping me promote the application, Michael Beeby, Al Palmer and Terry Foote: For their agreement to utilize the product and for believing in its potential,
And thanks to all those who have tested the application and provided their comments.
